         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Five manuscript copies of 
         <title render="italic">The American Version,</title>
            <title render="italic">Southern Tenant Farmer,</title>
            <title render="italic">Vengeance of the Earth (All Night
         Long),</title>
            <title render="italic">We Are the Living;</title>1970-1979,
         newspaper and magazine clippings re lectures, plays and books
         of Erskine Caldwell; and photographs.</p>
      </scopecontent>
